        "cooked": "<p>Think there is a typo in the BOSL2 docs - you need to include the beziers.scad<br>\nvis\u2026</p>\n<p>include &lt;BOSL2/std.scad&gt;<br>\ninclude&lt;BOSL2/beziers.scad&gt;</p>\n<p>bez = [[0,0,0], [0,50,0], [0,50,50], [0,100,50]];<br>\npath_extrude(bezier_curve(bez, 128)) square(10);</p>",
